
BOWER INSTALL

	1. npm install -g bower
	2. cd to <project>/public/
	3. sudo bower install angular --alow-root
	4. sudo bower install underscore --allow-root
	
	/** Create bower install file */
	
	6. sudo bower init --allow-root
	7. follow the form < aka press enter a bunch >
	8. now bower.json file appears
	
	/** Install from bower.json file */

	9. sudo bower install --allow-root 

	/** Search for packages */

	10. sudo bower search angular
